    <span id="dnn_ctr420221_WelcomeText_lblWelcomeText" class="WelcomeText_Label">We are 3SX Performance Automotive and we focus on quality cars at 
reasonable prices. We made our name selling high performance products for imports for the last 13 years. Now we are branching out and using our knowledge of all things automotive to bring you quality used vehicles. Although we cut out teeth on performance vehicles we offer vehicles for all walks of life Trucks, Vans, Cars, SUVs, Hot Rods, to Imports we truly do it all. Being car enthusiasts we are able stock our lot with cars that we feel are genuinely good vehicles. Cars you will truly enjoy driving, when going from point A to B is not enough! Are you looking for a specific vehicle? Don't see one in our inventory? We can locate just about any kind of car you could imagine. Financing available if needed.
